      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING DELORIS (3) is looking to continue her winning ways off a scintillating 22.53 win at this track. In form and rates on top again. ELECTRIC ASSENT (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at Gosford over 388m behind Ascend Fern (23.03) in a NG. Was in the money the start prior. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can figure in the finish. BARRAMUNDI LOU (2) ran a swift 22.78 when placed over 400m at this track last start in a Grade 3/4. Has the ability and can measure up. SONGAR OSCAR (8) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts ago but finished seventh last time (16.25) at this track. Is yet to taste defeat in two starts from this draw.",
